column5: Check out these photos and read the caption under the first one before going to the bottom one.              Look at the picture above and you can see where this guy broke through the guardrail, right side where the people are standing on the road (pointing). The pick-up was traveling from right to left when it crashed through the guardrail. It flipped end-over-end, across the culvert outlet, and landed right side up on the left side of the culvert, facing the opposite direction from which he was traveling.      Now look at the 2nd picture below...
Holy Crap !!!  If I was driving they'd never get the smell out of the seats...   Hookset.
Wow! Sure has horseshoes up his a--!
Forget the horseshoes....I think it was the whole horse.......
WOW..Thats amazing, talk about being your lucky day !!!!...i hope he buys a lottery ticket after that,as well as using up most of your 9 lives....i think he used all of them !!!...
wow that's messed up, he was one lucky fellow,  or was he.... maybe it was a botched suicide attempt
LOL who needs airbags when you have something soft and warm available.
Looks like a Chevy! Dependable truck, right there!  Take that Ford! lol
But.... was he wearing his seatbelt?
I don't think I' like to be where those paramedics are standing too much.  Joey
I always thought a jersey wall would make a good ramp.
time for better gaurd rails over that bridge lol  what a lucky guy  cheers!
